episodes.title: The END of Tiktoker Who Got Scammed by a Cult | Rubee Lana
episodes.description:
Meet Rubee Lana, a once-beloved TikToker with over five million followers whose life took a terrifying turn after she was allegedly recruited by a mysterious group calling themselves Free Him Now. Overnight, she vanished from the internet deleting all her social media accounts, cutting off her family, and moving across the country to join what many now call a modern-day cult.

In this documentary, we uncover how Rubee went from a vibrant TikTok star to a manipulated victim of religious exploitation. Through leaked clips, her emotional confession, and online investigations, we expose the shocking truth behind the Free Him Now ministry a so-called spiritual movement that preyed on young influencers in the name of God.

Was Rubee truly brainwashed, or was she seeking meaning in the wrong place? And how many others have fallen for the same trap?
From her heartbreaking disappearance to her emotional escape and eventual healing, this video dives deep into the dark world of digital cults and the dangers of blind faith online.

If you’re fascinated by true-story exposés, influencer scandals, and social media investigations, this is one you don’t want to miss.

Watch till the end, subscribe for more RKH Media documentaries, and comment your thoughts on Rubee’s story below.
